Compilation:

* Windows (MinGw)
  a) download and install MinGw
     http://www.mingw.org/
  b) run 
     make -f Makefile.w32
     
* UNIX / Linux (Console)
  a) run
     make -f Makefile.con  

* DOS (Turbo C 2.01)
  a) download and install Turbo C:
     http://edn.embarcadero.com/article/20841
  b) download and extract Tetris sources into tetris directory
  c) copy *.BGI drivers from Turbo C directory to tetris sources directory
  d) run Turbo C
  e) go to Project->Project name and choose TETRIS.PRJ
  f) go to Compile->Make EXE file

* ZX Spectrum (Z88DK)
  a) download and install Z88DK
     http://www.z88dk.org
  b) run 
     make -f Makefile.zx

 * ZX81 (Z88DK)
   Requirements: HiRes = WRX, RamPack = 32kB 
  a) download and install Z88DK
     http://www.z88dk.org
  b) run 
     make -f Makefile.81
